title: Bank of America’s Great Reset | Guests: Bill O’Reilly & Jeff Brown | 2/12/21
description:
Bank of America’s new rules take steps to sidestep the Constitution and Congress to implement the Green New Deal and Great Reset themselves. “The Mandalorian” star Gina Carano was fired over a Holocaust reference, but is there a double standard going on? Glenn says Disney is no longer Disney. Sen. Ted Cruz joins to discuss the impeachment trial and how the media has become propaganda outlets. Twitter has banned Project Veritas. Bill O’Reilly talks the impeachment trial, the Democrats’ accelerating agenda, and Trump’s future. The media are finally reporting Andrew Cuomo’s nursing home scandal. High tech expert Jeff Brown joins to discuss newly filed “Navy UFO patents." Are flying cars a future possibility?
